		<title>Welcome Email</title>
		<style>
			body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;
			background-color: #f9f9f9; } .email-container { max-width: 700px;
			margin: 50px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 15px;
			box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); overflow: hidden; }
			.header { background-color: #000; color: white; text-align: center;
			padding: 30px; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; } .body {
			padding: 30px; color: #333; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.8; }
			.highlight-box { margin: 30px auto; padding: 20px 30px;
			background-color: #f1f1f1; border: 3px dashed #000; text-align:
